		<span id="title-177660081" class="story-title"> <a   href="//news.slashdot.org/story/25/05/20/1554221/americas-college-towns-go-from-boom-to-bust">America's College Towns Go From Boom To Bust</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://www.msn.com/en-us/money/markets/america-s-college-towns-go-from-boom-to-bust/ar-AA1F1eaS"  title="External link - https://www.msn.com/en-us/money/markets/america-s-college-towns-go-from-boom-to-bust/ar-AA1F1eaS" target="_blank"> (msn.com) </a></span></span>

		
		
